<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know when so let&rsquo;s have the best times of our lives until then. Let&rsquo;s enjoy the world, let&rsquo;s enjoy the football, let&rsquo;s enjoy the journey and it&rsquo;s what we did so far &ndash; it was a good time.&rdquo;
